  https://git-scm.com
  Version control that tracked every iteration of this project from
  day one.

GitHub — GitHub, Inc.
  https://github.com
  Where this project lives, where releases ship, and where the
  community gathers.

concurrently — Kimmo Brunfeldt
  License: MIT
  https://github.com/open-cli-tools/concurrently
  Runs our dev server and Electron process in parallel. Small tool,
